profile:
SteriGleam Janitorial Corp. is a commercial cleaning company providing custodian services to office spaces, medical health centres, dental clinics, pharmacies, retail stores, and apartment buildings. While other companies clean, we offer value to our customers by incorporating modern laboratory and medical sterilization and sanitation procedures within our processes.

All of our staff continually trains in the latest compliance methods and are insured and bonded. In addition to our janitorial services, we provide third-party sterilization compliance testing through adenosine triphosphate (ATP) bioluminescence measurements, laboratory pathogen surface analysis, and quality medical and janitorial supplies from national vendors.

We have over 15 years of experience in maintaining intensive care units, operating rooms, emergency departments, and medical analysis clinics.

profile: We specialize in Vacation Home Cleaning. This is all we do! Between handling bookings, responding to & checking-in guests, running a short-term vacation rental can become a full-time job. services:
WHAT'S INCLUDED IN A VACATION HOME CLEAN

We offer four types of cleaning packages. The Urban Cleaner specializes in providing cleaning services for vacation homes and short-term rentals. Hosts and Property Managers can rest assure their property is cleaned and ready for their next guest. 
We want to give you an overview as well as the details of the services we provide and the differences between our cleanings.

THE URBAN CLEANER SUPER HOST 
On a budget! It would help if you had a basic clean in between guest. The Urban Cleaner Host gets the job done.
THE URBAN CLEANER HOST PLUS
This service is for those who provide a boutique feel for their guest. These host will enjoy extra services such as customized staging and restocking with priority scheduling.

POST STAY
Instant notification when the cleaner is on their way, starts and finishes the job.
Make sure the guests left the property in the condition in which they found it. 
Report any new visible damages in the property and take pictures 
INSPECTION
All lights turn on
All faucets work, and toilets flush
Kitchen major appliances work
Thermostat adjusted to preferred settings
Check Wi-Fi is up and running and all tv’s turn on.
AUTOMATED SCHEDULING 
Automate cleaning bookings by syncing with our company calendar, and our system automatically assigns a cleaner to take care of your property on the day of check-out.

OTHER LIVING SPACES:

All surfaces dusted (including cobwebs, ceiling fans, picture frames, lamps, etc.)
Light organizing
Customize staging 
Wipe touch points (light switch, doors and doorknobs and remote controls)
Spot wipe minor smudges on walls if moisture tolerant 
Clean mirrors and glass tables
Cushions and pillows fluffed and straightened
Dust baseboards
Vacuum and wash all floors
Empty and clean all wastebaskets and replace liner from host supplies 






KITCHEN:
All surfaces dusted
Light organizing and restock dish soap and sponge if needed
Restock  and top up all kitchen cleaning supplies from the host supply cabinet
Dishes loaded in the dishwasher ( and taken out and put away in cupboards).
Remove perishables from the fridge and wipe shelves
Clean appliances exterior facings (stovetop, oven, fridge, microwave inside and out, dishwasher) 
Clean inside Oven only if deep clean has recently been 
Wipe cabinet facings
Wipe small appliances toaster, coffee maker, hot water kettle, blender etc.
Wipe table and chairs
Wipe and sanitize countertops
Empty and clean all wastebaskets and replace liner from host supplies 





BATHROOMS:
All surfaces dusted
Light organizing
Restocking Hand Soap and Toilet Paper 
Restock and top up all Bathroom supplies from the host supply cabinet
Wipe cabinet facings
Clean mirrors
Clean and sanitize showers, bathtubs and toilets and sinks 
Place fresh towels on the towel rack and a roll of toilet paper (from host stock)


BEDROOMS
All surfaces dusted
Light organizing
Make beds and change linens
Wipe mirrors and glass fixtures


LAUNDRY
We wash one load of linen and towels and transfer them into a dryer. Laundry is left in the dryer. We do not wait for the dryer cycle to complete to make the beds/ fold or hang towels.
